      <title>中国部分行业开始出现牛市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-13/china-begins-witnessing-bull-markets-in-some-sectors-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国多个行业的牛市已经开始。这表明，在政府努力提振经济和市场的情况下，投资者看到了当前估值的上升空间。阿布舍克·维什诺伊 (Abhishek Vishnoi) 接受彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-13/china-begins-witnessing-bull-markets-in-some-sectors-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:56:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渣打银行表示中国市场“看起来并没有那么糟糕”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-13/china-market-not-looking-so-bad-stanchart-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打财富管理股票策略主管 Daniel Lam 分享了他对中国和日本市场的看法以及他看到的机遇。他在“彭博社黎明：亚洲”节目中发表讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-13/china-market-not-looking-so-bad-stanchart-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:41:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称中国开发商万科正在与银行进行债务互换谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-13/china-vanke-said-to-be-in-debt-swap-talks-with-banks-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，由于对其偿债能力的担忧加剧，国家支持的开发商万科集团一直面临压力，该公司正在与银行就债务互换进行谈判，以帮助其避免有史以来的首次债券违约。洛雷塔·陈 (Lorretta Chen) 接受彭博电视台报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-13/china-vanke-said-to-be-in-debt-swap-talks-with-banks-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>垃圾债券空头并不相信“这次不一样”的口号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/a-junk-bond-bear-isn-t-buying-this-time-it-s-different-mantra</link>
      <description><![CDATA[到 2024 年，几乎所有地区的垃圾债券都会击败风险较低的债券，但 Vontobel Holding AG 的一位策略师表示，他正在避开该资产类别。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/a-junk-bond-bear-isn-t-buying-this-time-it-s-different-mantra</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:22:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BlueBay最大的宏观赌注是做空日本政府债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/bluebay-s-biggest-macro-bet-is-shorting-japan-government-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大皇家银行 BlueBay 资产管理公司已将出售日本政府债券作为日本央行下周可能加息的预期的首要赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/bluebay-s-biggest-macro-bet-is-shorting-japan-government-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:09:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>HQ Capital 聘请 Ardian 的 Michael Hu 负责亚洲扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/hq-capital-hires-ardian-s-michael-hu-to-head-asia-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[HQ Capital 是一家专注于中小型市场投资的欧洲私募股权公司，聘请 Ardian SAS 前高管 Michael Hu 担任亚洲区主管，并在新加坡开设了新办事处，以寻求在该地区开发财富。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/hq-capital-hires-ardian-s-michael-hu-to-head-asia-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在监管机构的审查下，流入印度衍生品的外国资金激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/foreign-flows-to-india-derivatives-swell-amid-regulator-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管监管机构加大了对冲基金和富人匿名投资的难度，但通过一种不起眼的离岸衍生品流入印度的外国资金仍在增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/foreign-flows-to-india-derivatives-swell-amid-regulator-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>行业报告指出美国库存下降，石油价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于行业报告指出美国原油库存减少，抵消了欧佩克摇摆不定的减产，油价在连续四天下跌后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 23:29:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 获胜，阿根廷完成 500 亿美元债务互换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/argentina-swaps-50-billion-of-local-debt-to-push-out-repayments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷成功地将今年到期的约 77% 比索债务换成较长期票据，这为哈维尔·米莱总统赢得了胜利，因为他积极采取行动支撑公共财政并稳定容易发生危机的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/argentina-swaps-50-billion-of-local-debt-to-push-out-repayments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 22:44:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本工资谈判进展缓慢，亚洲股市涨跌互现：市场收官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市涨跌互现，美国创纪录交易日的积极情绪被东京工资谈判所抵消，早期迹象有利于日本央行转向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 22:27:05 GMT</pubDate>
